I faced the same problem. I don&#39;t know exactly why it occurred, but something with storing the Model went wrong. But I managed to reconnect with the following procedure:

 1. Copy the whole folder of the Project and store it somewhere 
 2. In the new folder delete the .original.alp-File
 3. Rename the .alp-File
 4. then open the Renamed .alp-File in an text-editor

In that file you&#39;ll find something like that:

